ttom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">Certificate of Supply chain Management program will be received from Melbourne Metropolitan College (MMC) which is a Registered Training Organization (RTO) in Australia.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">CareersHub with the collaboration of MMC is running this professional postgraduate diploma program.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">Nowadays, degrees are becoming ever more commonplace, so it is important to make your Resume stand out from the rest. Postgraduate Diploma will assist you in your working or corporate life rather than acquiring new skills, but it will add a few competitive advantages over the other candidates who are potentially applying for the same roles.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">In general, the average Postgraduate Diploma course will cost less than its Masters equivalent degree or courses.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">While you are doing a postgraduate diploma in our Institution, you will get in touch with so many corporate professionals from other or same sector considering yours, this will help you to develop your networking skill.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">This will help any individual to secure his or her job & get a better opportunity in the same or different field.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">Flexible, affordable & International professional certificates</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">Excellent & quality study materials & practice questions.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">Experienced &highly qualified industr