 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">While you are doing a postgraduate diploma in our Institution, you will get in touch with so many corporate professionals from other or same sector considering yours, this will help you to develop your networking skill.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">This will help any individual to secure his or her job & get a better opportunity in the same or different field.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">Flexible, affordable & International professional certificates</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">Excellent & quality study materials & practice questions.</p><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \"Helvetica Neue\", sans-serif;\">Experienced &highly qualified industr