INSERT INTO `services` (`id`, `title`, `description`, `service_img`, `status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 'Our Program Is Designed Just For You', 'People who have the guts to leave the job of sure income and leave the desire to do a job and dream of becoming a digital entrepreneur but want proper guidance cannot move towards it. In that case, we create that way for the fresh graduates and make the freelancers more polish to prove their ability by giving them befitting instructions. That is the work we do. In other words, we provide technical education for beginners and those who already have a little knowledge of technical education.   \r\nThe thought may enter into your mind that, as a novice or new freelancer, I won\'t be able to complete this program with these highly skilled mentors. But let me assure you, our programs are designed so that anybody with little or no knowledge will be able to cope with them and learn from them because we have outlined the program with a friendly syllabus and cozy training environment.', '111020200517485faa227c116d6.jpg', 1, '2020-11-10 05:17:48', '2020-11-09 23:17:48'),
(2, 'Skill Ensures A Huge Source of Income', 'Our program\'s strategy is planned to ensure enough earnings after efficiently finishing the program, of course, being skilled. We will take you to that height, and you can put your trust upon us in this issue that if you can gain skill enough, you will get work quickly as there is a tremendous demand for those who have the necessary talent. So, there will not be a fear of not earning enough to maintain your family or resign from your job.', '111020200517585faa22867c192.jpg', 1, '2020-11-10 05:17:58', '2020-11-09 23:17:58'),
(3, 'Enlighten Yourself', 'Everyone has the right to take his/her life in the right direction. They can live a happy life and try to make other\'s lives fulfil the same happiness. This is the beginning of changing the world into a lovely place to live happily. To do so, change your life as a digital entrepreneur, and it is our commitment that we will help you at every stage of your adventure. Our creative, modern, and technology-based program has got all the necessary elements to fulfil your destiny.', '111020200517325faa226c89bde.jpg', 1, '2020-11-10 05:17:32', '2020-11-09 23:17:32'),
(4, 'Believe In Yourself', '\"Confident leaders are better able to persuade investors, clients, and partners. They\'re generally regarded as more authoritative and trustworthy by their employees, making them more effective as team leaders and managers.\"\r\nBefore starting anything at first, you will need a lot of self-confidence. If you can believe in yourself, then you can overcome any obstacle, whether it seems to be impossible at first. You may feel reluctant, \"Is it possible for me to become a digital entrepreneur? \"The answer is yes if you believe in yourself. \r\n\r\nS/He always becomes the winner, who can think that \'Yes, I can, and I will\". We all make mistakes at the very beginning of any work. But our mistakes prevent us from making other errors and complete the job flawlessly. So, self-confidence plays a vital role here.', '111020200517255faa2265344b4.jpg', 1, '2020-11-10 05:17:25', '2020-11-09 23:17:25'),
(7, 'Foresee Your Success', 'You will be able to predict your success after mastering the program with us. The up growing success rate of a digital entrepreneur will never give you other options to think about some other profession except a digital entrepreneur. It is being spread out worldwide day by day, and it will never stop growing. Because of the importance of a digital entrepreneur, the world is more prone to brace it as a blessing in every digitally ongoing world sector. The acceptance of digital entrepreneurs is more and more welcomed every day. Thus, you will become a leader for those seeking the opportunity to become a digital entrepreneur.', '111020200517405faa227403667.jpg', 1, '2020-11-10 05:17:40', '2020-11-09 23:17:40');

